 bygging p\u00e5 egne tomter p\u00e5 Moholt, i Klostergata og eventuelt p\u00e5 kommunalt eide tomer p\u00e5 Sorgenfri.", "Tilskuddene til studentboliger de siste \u00e5rene har ligget p\u00e5 1000 for hele landet. Mange mener n\u00e5 at tallet m\u00e5 opp i 2000 for \u00e5 n\u00e5 de nasjonale m\u00e5l."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "3fe03c8db9861c74d2452fca819d41876ccf86eba59da62fa4f9b2757a58db37"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-10-27T12:37:16.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Studentsamskipnaden dropper planene om 200 nye studentboliger i den planlagte gigantbygget Trondheimsporten."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article7078213.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/front.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/7f654441a5223009f14e35aeffb241cefde9972e.jpg?596ddf8c"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["SiT dropper Trondheimsporten -adressa.no", "For kostbart", "Tilbakeslag"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "7f654441a5223009f14e35aeffb241cefde9972e"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["planer", "studentbolig", "bygge", "boliger", "tilskudd"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["kunnskapsdepartementet", "lerkendal", "studentsamskipnaden", "klostergata", "moholt", "trondheimsporten", "sorgenfri", "sit"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["norge", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": 